{"_id":"wH4jwy22p7rxqGzK","name":"Jaws of the Ghoul","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/head/greathelm-slotted-steel.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>(Requires attunement)</em></p>\n<p><em>This nightmarish great helm is adorned in red abyssal scripture and bears a visor that resembles a mouth of jagged teeth. Some say the helmet itself comes alive to tear away at its wearers foes.</em></p>\n<hr />\n<p>While attuned and wearing the helm you can make a bite attack using yourbonus action dealing 1d6 plus your proficiency modifier in piercing damage. This attack uses your Strength of Dexterity modifier to hit, and is considered magical for overcoming damage resistance. </p>\n<p><strong>Necrosis.</strong> When you roll a critical hit with your bite attack it deals necrotic damage instead of piercing, and the target must roll a Constitution saving throw *(DC:15)*. The target is paralyzed until the end of their next turn on a failure, and is not on a success.</p>\n<p> </p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Relics of the Realm","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d6","piercing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":15,"scaling":"flat"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"clothing","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":0,"stealth":false,"proficient":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"tQqupPK3rQvebWSm":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Ite